racters move directly away from their \'93home\'94 and out into the realm.  Monsters only move one clearing (walking) or one tile (flyers).  Once they move off the edge of the map, they are removed from play.  {\rtlch\ltrch\hich\i\loch\i Exception}:  if there are characters in the same tile
 as a prowling generated monster, these will immediately move to the same clearing as the player, like any other monster.  In some cases, a generated monster has special behaviors when moving.}
